<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"/>
  <title>Real Time Calling Analysis Dashboard</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/styles.css"/>
</head>
<body>
<div class="landing">
  <div class="landing__hero">
    <div class="landing__hero-badge">Live Analytics Platform</div>
    <h1 class="landing__title">Real Time Calling<br/>Analysis Dashboard</h1>
    <p class="landing__subtitle">Fetch data and analyse your business — across AI dialing, CDR routing, vendor leads, and hourly traffic in one unified view.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="landing__grid">
    <a class="landing__card" href="/analytics/overview">
      <div class="landing__card-icon landing__card-icon--blue">01</div>
      <span class="landing__card-title">Overview Call Analysis</span>
      <span class="landing__card-desc">19 KPIs across all call sources — AI dialed, 382, TBI, leads cost, transfers, human answer rate and more.</span>
      <span class="landing__card-arrow">Explore &rarr;</span>
    </a>

    <a class="landing__card" href="/analytics/server">
      <div class="landing__card-icon landing__card-icon--cyan">02</div>
      <span class="landing__card-title">Server Wise Analysis</span>
      <span class="landing__card-desc">Per-IP server breakdown of calls, ASR, ACD, cost and traffic volume across 382 and TBI infrastructure.</span>
      <span class="landing__card-arrow">Explore &rarr;</span>
    </a>

    <a class="landing__card" href="/analytics/vendor">
      <div class="landing__card-icon landing__card-icon--amber">03</div>
      <span class="landing__card-title">Lead / Vendor Wise Analysis</span>
      <span class="landing__card-desc">Vendor lead volumes, costs, call counts, transfer rates and paid conversion — ranked and compared side-by-side.</span>
      <span class="landing__card-arrow">Explore &rarr;</span>
    </a>

    <a class="landing__card" href="/analytics/hourly">
      <div class="landing__card-icon landing__card-icon--rose">04</div>
      <span class="landing__card-title">Hourly Business Analysis</span>
      <span class="landing__card-desc">Hour-by-hour call volume heatmap, peak period detection and cost trends across all dialing sources.</span>
      <span class="landing__card-arrow">Explore &rarr;</span>
    </a>

    <a class="landing__card" href="/analytics/ai-summary">
      <div class="landing__card-icon landing__card-icon--cyan">05</div>
      <span class="landing__card-title">AI Summary</span>
      <span class="landing__card-desc">Total dialed, transfers, CDR attempts and paid transfers for any date and EDT/EST time window — across all 3 carriers.</span>
      <span class="landing__card-arrow">Explore &rarr;</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="landing__footer">
    <a href="/dashboard" class="landing__footer-link">Open legacy call table &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
